{"tid":351881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油麻地至旺角要慢駛　觀塘線4日兩故障","createTime":"2017-08-08T11:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T11:50:34.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59bfa1328b38a834fe55ec547358cae6b103813e","tid":351881,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"港鐵觀塘線繼上星期六（5日）後，4日內再度發生信號故障。港鐵今晚約7時在網頁公布，觀塘線列車駛經油麻地站至旺角站路段時需要慢駛，來往黃埔站及調景嶺站的行車時間，預計需要額外5至10分鐘。油麻地站往返調景嶺站的列車要每4分鐘一班，黃埔站往返油麻地站則每10分鐘一班。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵稱，現時觀塘線月台上的乘客較多，候車時間亦會較長，呼籲乘客為行程預留充裕時間。港鐵職員現正進行搶修工作。"},{"pid":"1ff25500b7759437aee2a93529154ebd72e06848","tid":351881,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"150%使用率<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f936673f2a0bd9fdff9f62a8eb2c3c4418897ef","tid":351881,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ee29701483695c3d230a7e8b974f05fb1775bd","tid":351881,"uid":10707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/194956_91d6b2712524a6f01f4259572601967e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F194956_91d6b2712524a6f01f4259572601967e.jpg&h=9f95266b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等下洗死咩香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}